ak|Right-arm off break]]\n|Province No. 3\n| A\n|ODI, T20I\n|77\n|-\n|[[Karan KC]]\n|{{age|1991|10|10}}\n|Right-handed\n|[[Fast bowling|Right-arm fast]]\n|[[APF Club|Armed Police Force Club]]\n|B\n|ODI, T20I\n|33\n|-\n|[[Sompal Kami]]||{{age|1996|02|02}}|| Right-handed ||[[Fast bowling|Right-arm fast-medium]]\n|[[Tribhuwan Army Club]]\n| A\n|ODI, T20I\n|10\n|-\n|[[Pawan Sarraf]]\n|{{age|2000|04|5}}\n|Right-handed\n|[[Off break|Right-arm off break]]\n|[[APF Club|Armed Police Force Club]]\n|\n|ODI, T20I\n| 22\n|-\n|[[Kushal Malla]]\n|{{age|2004|3|5}}\n|Left-handed\n|[[Left-arm orthodox spin]]\n|[[Tribhuwan Army Club]]\n|\n| T20I\n| 5\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" |  Pace Bowlers\n|-\n|[[Avinash Bohara]]\n|{{age|1997|07|30}}\n|Right-handed\n|[[Fast bowling|Right-arm medium]]\n|[[APF Club|Armed Police Force Club]]\n|\n|T20I\n|3\n|-\n! colspan=\"6\" |  Spin Bowlers\n!\n!\n|-\n|[[Basanta Regmi]]\n|{{age|1986|4|6}}\n|Right handed\n|[[Left-arm orthodox spin]]\n|[[APF Club|Armed Police Force Club]]\n|A\n|ODI, T20I\n| 9\n|-\n| [[Sandeep Lamichhane]] || {{age|2000|8|2}} || Right handed|| [[Leg break]] [[googly]]\n||| A\n|ODI, T20I\n|25\n|-\n|[[Lalit Rajbanshi]]\n|{{age|1999|2|27}}\n|Right handed\n|[[Left-arm orthodox spin]]\n|[[Nepal Police Club]]\n|B\n|ODI, T20I\n|27\n|-\n|[[Sushan Bhari]]\n|{{age|1995|3|6}}\n|Left handed\n|[[Left-arm orthodox spin]]\n|[[Tribhuwan Army Club]]\n|C\n|ODI, T20I\n|12\n|-\n|}\n\n====Other Contracted players====\n====Grade B====\n*[[Anil Kumar Sah]]\n*[[Lalit Bhandari]]\n\n====Grade C====\n*[[Subash Khakurel]]\n*[[Binod Bhandari]]\n*[[Sunil Dhamala]]\n*[[Sagar Pun]]\n*Kishore Mahato\n\n==Coaching staff==\n* Head Coach: Vacant\n{{flagicon|NEP}} Jagat Tamata (Interim)\n\n* Assistant Coach: Vacant\n\n* Batting coach:  Vacant\n\n* Bowling Coach:  Vacant\n\n* Fielding Coach:  Vacant\n\n* Manager:  {{flagicon|NEP}} Madhav Kumar Karmacharya\n\n* Physiotherapist: {{flagicon|NEP}} Vikram Neupane\n\n* Trainer: Vacant\n\n* Analyst: {{flagicon|NEP}} Raman Shiwakoti\n\n